tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE retail_store_sales (
    store_id INT,
    sale_date DATE,
    sale_time TIME,
    total_sales DECIMAL(10, 2)
)
CREATE TABLE store_sales (   sale_id INT,   sale_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),   sale_date TIMESTAMP,   store_location VARCHAR(50) );
CREATE TABLE store_inventory (   product_id INT,   product_name VARCHAR(50),   stock_quantity INT,   unit_price DECIMAL(8, 2) );
CREATE TABLE store_hours (   store_location VARCHAR(50),   day_of_week VARCHAR(10),   opening_time TIME,   closing_time TIME );
